ps.\\r\\n\\r\\n    Thank you so much for all of the wonderful comments following the release of Prince Harry and Ms. Meghan Markle\'s engagement photographs. The couple are so grateful for the warm and generous messages they have received during such a happy time in their lives. As a way to say thank you, they have decided to share this candid photograph from the day of their portrait sittings directly with all of you. A post shared by  Kensington Palace (@kensingtonroyal) on Dec 21, 2017 at 6:00am PST\\nEt une fois arriv\\u00e9 \\u00e0 Nice, le couple a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 accueilli par la police fran\\u00e7aise qui s\\u2019est charg\\u00e9e de leur s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 pendant leur s\\u00e9jour sur le territoire. Des vacanciers presque comme les autres\\u2026\\n\",\"relatedLink\":\"\",\"image\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/img.20mn.fr\\/ht20WJBoRLSKxEcVLFJTAQ\\/830x532_prince-harry-fiancee-meghan-markle-fait-premier-bain-foule\",\"height\":\"830\",\"width\":\"532\"},\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"20 Minutes avec agences\"},\"keywords\":[\"mariage princier\",\"prince harry\",\"France\",\"Meghan Markle\"]}\n    </script>\n\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\"@context\":\"https:\\/\\/schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"item\":{\"@id\":\"http:\\/\\/www.20minutes.fr\\/people\\/\",\"name\":\"People\"}}]}\n    </script>\n                                        \n\n            <!-- Googletag -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n    var googletag = googletag || {};\n    googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];\n    (function() {\n        var gads = document.createElement(\"script\");\n        gads.async = true;\n        gads.type = \"text/javascript\";\n        var useSSL = \"https:\" == document.location.protocol;\n        gads.src = (useSSL ? \"https:\" : \"http:\") + \"//www.googletagservices.com/tag/js/gpt.js\";\n        var node = document.getElementsByTa