\"lnid\":\"author\"}}\' href=\"/author/claire-terve\">\n                                        <span class=\"author-card__details__name\">\n                                        Claire Tervé\n                                        </span>\n                                    </a>\n                                    <span class=\"author-card__social-container desktop-only\">\n                                                                                                                                                            </span>\n                                                                    </span>\n                                <span class=\"author-card__microbio desktop-only\">\n                                    Claire Tervé\n                                </span>\n                            </div>\n                        </li>\n                                                </ul>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n                    \n    </div>\n    \n                                                    \n                <div class=\"page__content\">\n                        \n    \n    <div class=\"page__content__row row--no-border\">\n                    <div class=\"col col--body-center\">\n                <div class=\"entry__below-entry \">\n                                            <article class=\"entry__content \">\n    \n        \n        \n                                                                                            \n        \n                \n    <div class=\"entry__body post-contents\" data-part=\"contents\">\n\n            <!-- ads_sharebox_260x60 -->\n    <div id=\"sharebox_260x60\" class=\n         \"advertisement sharebox_260x60\"  \"ad_spot desktop-only\">\n        \n    </div>\n\n                                                                \n        \n                    <p>MARIAGE - Ils se sont dit \"oui\". Le \"couple en or\" de la boxe form&eacute; par <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/news/tony-yoka/\" target=\"_blank\">Tony Yoka</a> et <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/news/estelle-mossely/\" target=\"_blank\">Estelle Mossely</a> s\'est mari&eacute;, dimanche 7 janvier &agrave; Paris. Les deux tourtereaux se sont pass&eacute;s la bague au doigt apr&egrave;s <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/2017/08/03/les-boxeurs-tony-yoka-et-estelle-mossely-sont-parents_a_23063109/?utm_hp_ref=fr-tony-yoka\" target=\"_blank\">la naissance de leur petit Ali</a>, en ao&ucirc;t dernier.</p>\n                        \n                                                            <!-- entry_paragraph_1_ad -->\n    <div id=\"entry_paragraph_1\" class=\"entry-body--paragraph-ad\">\n    	<div class=\"ad_spot \"\n	        >\n	              	</div>\n    </div>\n                                                                \n\n<p>\"It\'s time Baby\", a simplement annonc&eacute; le boxeur sur sa story Instagram dimanche. Un commentaire appos&eacute; sur un selfie des deux nouveaux mari&eacute;s. Resplendissante avec ses cheveux boucl&eacute;s et sa robe en dentelle, la m&eacute;daill&eacute;e d\'or arbore un grand sourire aux c&ocirc;t&eacute; de son mari, &eacute;l&eacute;gant dans son costume noir. D\'apr&egrave;s <em><a href=\"http://www.parismatch.com/People/Tony-Yoka-et-Estelle-Mossely-se-sont-dit-oui-1434029#utm_term=Autofeed&amp;utm_campaign=Echobox&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;xtor=CS2-14&amp;utm_source=Twitter&amp;link_time=1515403253\" target=\"_blank\">Paris Match</a></em>, la c&eacute;r&eacute;monie a eu lieu au Pavillon Royal, au bois de Boulogne.</p>\n                        \n                                                                                                <!-- entry_paragraph_2_ad -->\n    <div id=\"entry_paragraph_2\" class=\"entry-body--paragraph-ad\">\n    	<div class=\"ad_spot \"\n	        >\n	              	</div>\n    </div>\n                                                                \n\n<p>\n\n\n                                                                            \n\n\n    \n    <figure class=\"content-list-component image\">\n        <span class=\"share-bar-image-wrapper\" data-beacon=\'{\"p\":{\"mnid\":\"entry_image\"}}\'>\n            <img class=\"image__src\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/6fa0b48fc036fc40765a00fa2eb7c1c4/206008230/26771850_1136839089780733_150248834_o.png\">\n\n            <div class=\"share-bar share-bar--instream\">\n                <div class=\"share-bar__item pinterest\" data-type=\"pinterest\">\n                    <a class=\"share-bar__item-link bN icon-Social_Pinterest\" data-beacon=\'{\"p\":{\"lnid\":\"share_pinterest\"}}\'\n                    data-pin-custom=\"true\"\n                    href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </span>\n                    <span class=\"image__credit\">\n            @TonyYoka sur Instagram\n            </span>\n                    </figure>\n</p>\n                        \n                                \n\n<p>Le boxeur a &eacute;galement partag&eacute; la photos de leurs alliances.</p>\n                        \n                                \n\n<p>\n\n\n                                                                            \n\n\n    \n    <figure class=\"content-list-component image\">\n        <span class=\"share-bar-image-wrapper\" data-beacon=\'{\"p\":{\"mnid\":\"entry_image\"}}\'>\n            <img class=\"image__src\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/c07da3fc10dc78712059762171efd83a/206008261/26735735_1136839079780734_1713446111_o.png\">\n\n            <div class=\"share-bar share-bar--instream\">\n                <div class=\"share-bar__item pinterest\" data-type=\"pinterest\">\n                    <a class=\"share-bar__item-link bN icon-Social_Pinterest\" data-beacon=\'{\"p\":{\"lnid\":\"share_pinterest\"}}\'\n                    data-pin-custom=\"true\"\n                    href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"></a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </span>\n                    <span class=\"image__credit\">\n            @TonyYoka sur Instagram\n            </span>\n                    </figure>\n</p>\n                                                    \n                                \n\n<p>Invit&eacute; au mariage des deux m&eacute;daill&eacute;s d\'or de Rio, Cyril Hanouna a partag&eacute; une photos pour ses fans.</p>\n                        \n                                                            <!-- entry_paragraph_3_ad -->\n    <div id=\"entry_paragraph_3\" class=\"entry-body--paragraph-ad\">\n    	<div class=\"ad_spot \"\n	        >\n	              	</div>\n    </div>\n                                                                \n\n<center>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"fr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">Au mariage du frerot <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TonyYoka?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@TonyYoka</a> avant de vous retrouver Demain mes amours!!#selfront#kifdeouf#vousmaveztropmanque <a href=\"https://t.co/8fWoaZhJLL\">pic.twitter.com/8fWoaZhJLL</a></p>\n                        \n                                \n&mdash; Cyril Hanouna (@Cyrilhanouna) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Cyrilhanouna/status/950111622177140736?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">7 janvier 2018</a></blockquote>\n\n<p></p>\n                        \n                                \n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ce n\'est pas la premi&egrave;re fois qu\'Estelle Mossely et Tony Yoka choisissent les r&eacute;seaux sociaux pour annoncer leurs grandes nouvelles. Pour<a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/2017/08/03/les-boxeurs-tony-yoka-et-estelle-mossely-sont-parents_a_23063109/?utm_hp_ref=fr-tony-yoka\" target=\"_blank\"> la naissance de leur premier enfant</a>, Ali, le 2 ao&ucirc;t dernier, ils avaient post&eacute; une photos sur leurs comptes.</p>\n                        \n                                                            <!-- entry_paragraph_4_ad -->\n    <div id=\"entry_paragraph